    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People or corporate bodies who make windows; often, but not always, refers to makers of stained glass windows. To distinguish makers of stained glass windows, use "stained glass artists."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
